posting_body: ['MUST HAVE STRONG CREDIT!', 'NO EVICTIONS!', 'NO CRIMINAL RECORDS!', 'NO EXCEPTIONS!', 'PLEASE FIND THE EXACT PROPERTY ADDRESS 1/4 INCH UNDER THE MAP IN THE LISTING FOR YOUR REFERENCE!!!!!', 'CALL NOW!!!!!', 'PLEASE FIND THE EXACT PROPERTY ADDRESS 1/4 INCH UNDER THE MAP IN THE LISTING FOR YOUR REFERENCE!!!!!!', 'Email Me, Call Me, or Text!!!!', 'Shawn Kaminsky', 'show contact info', 'Tri-level 3 bedroom and 3 .5 bath town house with 2 car garage in Vistazo.', 'Unit overlooks the pool, pond and landscaped area.', 'Large master suite with balcony, walk in closet, Steam/Shower, and Whirlpool Spa.', 'Large Kitchen with Granite counters tops and all stainless steel appliances; accessible from living, dining & family room.', 'Flooring: Pergo and carpet.', 'Vistazo community is located off Spanish River Blvd in East Boca Raton, Florida; less than a mile 1/2 to the beach.', 'The construction of Vistazo was built to last; every town house is CBS construction on all three floors with barriers between each level in order to eliminate sound.', "The community boasts two pools, a state of the art fitness center and children's tot lot.", 'NOTE:', '1) Monthly Processing Fee $75 + rent OR online monthly payment with NO Processing Fee or by setting up automatic payments.', '2) $150 Cleaning fee will be held at end of moving time']
